        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:110mm; top:30mm; width:60mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Note the wire direction", "zh": "注意引线朝向" },
        "body": { "en": "Confirm the motor's wires face the direction shown before fixing the bracket.", "zh": "固定支架前，先确认电机引线朝向与图一致。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:110mm; top:60mm; width:60mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Leave the bolts loose", "zh": "螺栓先别拧紧" },
        "body": { "en": "Don't fully tighten the motor mount yet — you'll slide it later to tension the belt.", "zh": "电机座先别拧死——后面还要靠滑动电机座来张紧同步带。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:150mm; top:128mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ]
  },
