        "body": { "en": "Snug only — final torque comes after belt tensioning.", "zh": "先轻轻拧到贴紧就行——等同步带张紧后再拧死。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:150mm; width:78mm;"
      }
